  <brief_title>An 8 Week Depression Study In Adults Diagnosed With Major Depressive Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-Controlled, Fixed-Dose Study Evaluating the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of Two Doses (20mg and 60mg) of a Once-Daily Oral Formulation of GW353162 in Subjects With Major Depressive Disorder for a Treatment Period of Eight Weeks</official_title>
  <sponsors>
